      "content": "The answer is straightforward: it's assuredly, unequivocally, and absolutely anonymous. We've taken every precaution to ensure that the underlying mechanisms generating the pseudonyms are so obfuscated, they're unintelligible to even the most skilled cryptanalysts. Our utility patents explicitly guarantee that any resulting data associated with consumer identifiers is demonstrably, verifiably, and irrefutably anonymous. Regulators would be foolish to question our absolute commitment to irreproachable anonymity.",
